text: The Moving True Story of a Woman Ahead of Her Time (West Frisian title: Nynke) is a 2001 Dutch drama movie. Pieter Verhoeff directed the movie. Monic Hendrickx, Jeroen Willems, and Joke Tjalsma acted in it. ==Other websites== * Category:2001 drama movies Category:Dutch drama movies Category:Movies directed by Pieter Verhoeff
